      "value": "<div class=\"ddb\">\n<p>Up to three creatures of your choice that you can see within range must make &amp;Reference[cha]{Charisma} saving throws. Whenever a target that fails this saving throw makes an attack roll or a saving throw before the spell ends, the target must roll a d4 and subtract the number rolled from the attack roll or saving throw.</p>\n<p><strong>At Higher Levels.</strong> When you cast this spell using a spell slot of 2nd level or higher, you can target one additional creature for each slot level above 1st.</p>\n</div>",
